'''黑熊'''（英語：Matthew Tyler Musto，{{bd|1990年|11月27日||}}），[[美国|美国]][[歌手|歌手]]、词曲作者、唱片制作人。以艺名'''Blackbear'''为大众所知。<ref>{{Cite web|title=blackbear – Biography – Billboard|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/6078323/blackbear/biography|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2019-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729202238/https://www.billboard.com/artist/6078323/blackbear/biography|dead-url=no}}</ref>他共发行了五张录音室专辑，六张[[EP_(消歧義)|EP]]，一张混音带专辑以及两张合作专辑。

==职业经历==
===2006年–2014年: 早期===
Blackbear高中时，是[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]乐队Polaroid的[[歌手|歌手]]。他们发行了一张名叫《''Paint The Town''》的专辑，一张名叫《''Inside And Out''》的EP，和一张名叫《''The Cure Demo''》的[[Demo|Demo]]，<ref>{{cite web|title=Polaroid on PureVolume|url=http://www.purevolume.com/polaroidd|website=PureVolume|accessdate=5 December 2017|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180114193740/http://www.purevolume.com/polaroidd|archive-date=2018-01-14|url-status=dead|dead-url=no}}</ref>并与Leakmob公司签署了合约。<ref name="reverbnation.com">{{cite web|title=Mat Musto Rock from Atlanta, GA|url=https://www.reverbnation.com/matmusto|website=ReverbNation|accessdate=6 December 2017|language=en-us|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821003431/https://www.reverbnation.com/matmusto|dead-url=no}}</ref>Blackbear在9年级时[[辍学|辍学]]，专攻音乐。<ref name="complex">{{cite web |title=Rapper and R&B Singer Blackbear is Reinvention, Personified |url=https://www.complex.com/music/2018/04/rapper-and-r-and-b-singer-blackbear-is-reinvention-personified |website=Complex |accessdate=3 November 2018 |language=en |archive-date=2019-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226170732/https://www.complex.com/music/2018/04/rapper-and-r-and-b-singer-blackbear-is-reinvention-personified |dead-url=no }}</ref>

离开Polaroid乐队之后，Blackbear移居[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]与[[尼歐_(歌手)|尼歐]]合作，开始了他的个人事业。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://pigeonsandplanes.com/interviews/2017/11/blackbear-interview|title=The Pop Star Who Never Wanted to be Famous|last=Caitlin|website=Pigeons & Planes|accessdate=2020-07-13|archive-date=2018-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180909044236/https://pigeonsandplanes.com/interviews/2017/11/blackbear-interview|dead-url=no}}</ref>他在2008年发行了他的第一张EP《''Brightness''》，随后又发行了《''Contrast''》，并在2010年发行了《''Exposure''》。他与当时[[Woe,_Is_Me|Woe, Is Me]]乐队成员{{link-en|Tyler Carter}}发行了圣诞节歌曲，紧随其后的是单曲《''Douche Bag''》。2011年7月，Blackbear发行了《''Year of the Blackbear''》EP。同年秋天，他决定以'''Blackbear'''作为他的艺名，并在11月用这个艺名与[[麥克·波斯納|麥克·波斯納]]发行了单曲《''Marauder Music''》<ref>{{cite web|title=Internet Archive Search: creator%3A%22Matthew Tyler Musto%22|url=https://archive.org/search.php?query=creator%3A%22Matthew+Tyler+Musto%22|website=archive.org|accessdate=6 December 2017|language=en}}</ref>

===2015年:《''Deadroses''》和《''Help''》===
Blackbear于2015年2月14日发行了他的第一张完整专辑《''Deadroses''》，共包含10首歌曲，并获得了好评。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://rlgtcanada.com/2015/07/29/did-blackbear-discretely-drop-the-album-of-the-year/|title=Did Blackbear Discretely Drop The Album Of The Year?|date=29 July 2015|website=rlgtcanada.com|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714012235/https://rlgtcanada.com/2015/07/29/did-blackbear-discretely-drop-the-album-of-the-year/|dead-url=no}}</ref>主打歌曲《"Idfc"》在Billboard的R&B百大热门歌曲榜上上榜了一年多，并在[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]和[[Spotify|Spotify]]上获得了数百万播放量。截止2019年6月，《"Idfc"》在[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]上的播放量超过了2250万。《"Idfc (Tarro) Remix"》的播放量为1.92亿。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/6078323/blackbear/chart?f=1230&sort=position|title=Blackbear - Chart history - Billboard|website=www.billboard.com|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726134956/https://www.billboard.com/artist/6078323/blackbear/chart?f=1230&sort=position|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二首单曲《''90210''》由G-Easy演唱，在[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]获得了超过1100万的播放量，在[[Spotify|Spotify]]上获得了超过900万的播放量。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hamilton|first1=BreeAngela|title=Review: Deadroses by blackbear|url=http://coogradio.com/2015/02/review-deadroses-by-blackbear/|website=coogradio|publisher=Coogradio|accessdate=27 April 2016|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714040446/http://coogradio.com/2015/02/review-deadroses-by-blackbear/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="spotify.com">{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/2cFrymmkijnjDg9SS92EPM|title=blackbear|publisher=|accessdate=2020-07-13|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716071006/https://open.spotify.com/artist/2cFrymmkijnjDg9SS92EPM|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年5月，Blackbear的单曲《''NYLA''》被[[Netflix|Netflix]]上的纪录片[[Hot_Girls_Wanted|Hot Girls Wanted]]收录。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4382552/|title=Hot Girls Wanted|date=29 May 2015|publisher=|via=IMDb|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2020-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200311160320/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4382552/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

紧随在专辑《''Deadroses''》之后的是EP《''Dead''》，这张EP包含了一个新单曲《''Weak While Ur Around''》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/dead-acoustic-ep/id991111726|title=Dead (Acoustic) – EP by blackbear on iTunes|publisher=[[iTunes|iTunes]]|date=June 2, 2015|access-date=June 30, 2016|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914125750/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/dead-acoustic-ep/id991111726|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/dead-acoustic-ep/id991111726/|title=Dead (Acoustic) – EP by blackbear on Apple Music|publisher=|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2017-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914125750/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/dead-acoustic-ep/id991111726|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Blackbear于2015年11月27日发行了他的第二张完整专辑《''Help''》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/help/id1083607683|title=Help by blackbear on iTunes|publisher=[[iTunes|iTunes]]|date=November 27, 2015|access-date=November 27, 2015|archive-date=2018-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802223459/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/help/id1083607683|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2016年：《''Drink Bleach''》、《''Cashmere Noose''》和《''Mansionz''》 ===
2016年4月20日，Blackbear发行了他的第四张EP《''Drink Bleach''》，其中有歌曲《''Boyfriend''》，[[Mike_Posner|Mike Posner]]和[[P-Lo|P-Lo]]也参与了这张EP的制作。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/drink-bleach-ep/id1124677370|title=Drink Bleach – EP by blackbear on iTunes|publisher=[[iTunes|iTunes]]|date=April 20, 2016|access-date=April 20, 2016|archive-date=2018-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180802194648/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/drink-bleach-ep/id1124677370|dead-url=no}}</ref>

这一年，Blackbear与很多歌手合作，例如美国摇滚乐队Linkin Park以及Jacob Sartorius和Phoebe Ryan。他还参加了Hoodie Allen的[[巡演|巡演]]，该乐队的单曲《''Champagne and Pools''》由Blackbear演唱。他同时也加入了Super Duper Kyle和Tinashe的巡演。

2016年8月2日，Blackbear通过[[SoundCloud|SoundCloud]]发行了他的第五张EP《''Cashmere Noose''》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://soundcloud.com/iamblackbear/sets/cashmere-noose|title=cashmere noose|publisher=|accessdate=2020-07-14|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028023622/https://soundcloud.com/iamblackbear/sets/cashmere-noose|dead-url=no}}</ref>他通过自己的制作团队Bear Trap Records自己完成了EP的制作。EP最初包含了美国说唱歌手Mod Sun的一首歌曲《''Spent All My Money On Rick Owens Cargo Pants''》，但是Blackbear将这首歌移除，替换为《''Wanderlust''》和《''Flirt Right Back''》<ref>{{Citation|title=Blackbear (Ft. MOD SUN) – Spent All My Money On Rick Owens Cargo Pants|url=https://genius.com/Blackbear-spent-all-my-money-on-rick-owens-cargo-pants-lyrics|language=en|accessdate=2017-04-08|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409111430/https://genius.com/Blackbear-spent-all-my-money-on-rick-owens-cargo-pants-lyrics|dead-url=no}}</ref>《''Cashmere Noose''》仍然可以在Blackbear的SoundCloud页面上找到。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://soundcloud.com/iamblackbear/sets/cashmere-noose|title=cashmere noose|website=SoundCloud|language=en|access-date=2017-04-08|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028023622/https://soundcloud.com/iamblackbear/sets/cashmere-noose|dead-url=no}}</ref>《''Cashmere Noose''》的最终版本在iTunes上排行第六，R&B排行第一，在[[Beyoncé|Beyonce]]的歌曲《''[[Lemonade|Lemonade]]''》和[[Drake|Drake]]的歌曲《''[[Views|Views]]''》之上。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hiphopweeklyradio.com/chart-toppers-112216/|title=[CHART TOPPERS] This Week in Music Sales: Nov. 22, 2016 – Hip Hop Weekly Radio|publisher=}}</ref>

