== 个人生平 ==
Blackbear出生于[[戴通纳海滩|戴通纳海滩]]，小时候就移居到了[[棕榈海滩|棕榈海滩]]<ref name="Wiki Fact Check"/>他十几岁时又移居到了[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]，后来又搬到了[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]。

2016年4月，Blackbear因过度饮酒入院，被诊断为慢性胰腺炎。在他住院期间，他抽出了他的清醒时间，创作出了专辑《''Digital Druglord''》<ref>{{cite web |title=Blackbear Looked Death in The Eyes And Released His Best Album to Date |url=https://www.hypefresh.co/blackbear-looked-death-in-the-eyes-and-released-his-best-album-to-date/ |website=Hypefresh Inc |accessdate=23 January 2020 |date=25 May 2017 |archive-date=2020-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715151350/https://www.hypefresh.co/blackbear-looked-death-in-the-eyes-and-released-his-best-album-to-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=How a Near-Death Experience Helped blackbear Make His Most Successful Album Yet |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7785135/blackbear-digital-druglord-album-interview |website=Billboard |accessdate=23 January 2020 |archive-date=2020-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200628150314/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/7785135/blackbear-digital-druglord-album-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>2018年11月，Blackbear与品牌[[PopSockets|PopSockets]]合作，并将他的收益的50%捐赠给了致力于治疗慢性胰腺炎的非营利组织 Mission: Cure。<ref>{{cite web |title=im 1 of many w/ chronic pancreatitis mission : cure are closer everyday to finding a cure. donating half to them!http://popsockets.com/pages/blackbear pic.twitter.com/2wT20pp5Dn |url=https://twitter.com/iamblackbear/status/1063566734815195136?lang=en |website=Twitter |accessdate=23 January 2020 |language=en |date=16 November 2018}}</ref>

2019年9月25日，Blackbear宣布他和他的女友Michele Maturo预计在2020年1月生下他们的第一个孩子。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Shoemaker |first1=Whitney |title=blackbear and Michele Maturo announce pregnancy |url=https://www.altpress.com/news/blackbear-michele-maturo-pregnancy-baby-boy/ |website=Alternative Press |accessdate=4 October 2019 |date=26 September 2019 |archive-date=2019-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190928203812/https://www.altpress.com/news/blackbear-michele-maturo-pregnancy-baby-boy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年1月29日，Blackbear夫妻宣布其儿子Midnight Thomas Musto于2020年1月26日出生。<ref>{{cite web |title=blackbear on Instagram: “MIDNIGHT THOMAS MUSTO IS HERE im a papa im a daddy!!!!!!!! omg omg i havent stopp crying” |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B76uG3unKVS/ |website=Instagram |accessdate=30 January 2020 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Michele on Instagram: “Midnight Thomas Musto is here + healthy & weighs 7lb 3oz & arrived January 26th. No other way to describe how I feel besides perfect.…” |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B76l_XYnA54/ |website=Instagram |language=en}}</ref>

